\begin{chaptersum}
\begin{itemize}[nosep]
\item Single-seed results show qualitative patterns but can be misleading for stochastic models
\item Multi-seed study (160 simulations): female ICI+TKI achieves highest survival rate (65\%)
\item Mann-Whitney U tests show directional sex effects but lack statistical significance at $n=20$
\item Glucose consumption tipping point between rates 2.0 and 4.0 determines tumor fate
\end{itemize}
\end{chaptersum}